Roxanne Hart https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roxanne_Hart 0 Roxanne Hart (born July 27, 1952) is an American actress, best known for her roles as Brenda Wyatt in the 1986 film Highlander, and as Nurse Camille Shutt on the CBS medical drama series Chicago Hope (1994–1998). Hart also received Tony and Drama Desk Awards nominations for her stage works.
